originalSql:
WITH AvgOrderAmount AS (
    SELECT 
        o_custkey,
        AVG(o_totalprice) AS avg_totalprice
    FROM 
        orders
    GROUP BY 
        o_custkey
),
TopSuppliers AS (
    SELECT 
        ps_suppkey,
        SUM(ps_supplycost * ps_availqty) AS total_supplycost
    FROM 
        partsupp
    GROUP BY 
        ps_suppkey
    HAVING 
        SUM(ps_supplycost * ps_availqty) > (SELECT AVG(ps_supplycost * ps_availqty) FROM partsupp)
),
SupplierRegion AS (
    SELECT 
        s.s_suppkey, 
        r.r_name
    FROM 
        supplier s
    JOIN 
        nation n ON s.s_nationkey = n.n_nationkey
    JOIN 
        region r ON n.n_regionkey = r.r_regionkey
),
CustomerOrders AS (
    SELECT 
        c.c_custkey,
        COUNT(o.o_orderkey) AS order_count,
        MAX(o.o_totalprice) AS max_order_price
    FROM 
        customer c
    LEFT JOIN 
        orders o ON c.c_custkey = o.o_custkey
    GROUP BY 
        c.c_custkey
)
SELECT 
    c.c_custkey AS custkey,
    c.c_name,
    COALESCE(oa.avg_totalprice, 0) AS avg_order_amount,
    COALESCE(o.max_order_price, 0) AS max_order_value,
    sr.r_name AS supplier_region,
    CASE 
        WHEN o.order_count > 10 THEN 'High Value Customer'
        WHEN o.order_count BETWEEN 5 AND 10 THEN 'Medium Value Customer'
        ELSE 'Low Value Customer'
    END AS customer_segment
FROM 
    customer c
LEFT JOIN 
    AvgOrderAmount oa ON c.c_custkey = oa.o_custkey
LEFT JOIN 
    CustomerOrders o ON c.c_custkey = o.c_custkey
LEFT JOIN 
    TopSuppliers ts ON o.c_custkey = ts.ps_suppkey
LEFT JOIN 
    SupplierRegion sr ON ts.ps_suppkey = sr.s_suppkey
WHERE 
    c.c_acctbal IS NOT NULL
ORDER BY 
    avg_order_amount DESC, 
    max_order_value DESC

FROM (SELECT "customer"."c_custkey" AS "CUSTKEY", "customer"."c_name" AS "C_NAME", CASE WHEN "t1"."AVG_TOTALPRICE" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t1"."AVG_TOTALPRICE" AS DECIMAL(15, 2)) ELSE 0.00 END AS "AVG_ORDER_AMOUNT", CASE WHEN "t3"."MAX_ORDER_PRICE" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t3"."MAX_ORDER_PRICE" AS DECIMAL(15, 2)) ELSE 0.00 END AS "MAX_ORDER_VALUE", "t9"."R_NAME" AS "SUPPLIER_REGION", CASE WHEN "t3"."ORDER_COUNT" > 10 THEN 'High Value Customer  ' WHEN "t3"."ORDER_COUNT" >= 5 AND "t3"."ORDER_COUNT" <= 10 THEN 'Medium Value Customer' ELSE 'Low Value Customer   ' END AS "CUSTOMER_SEGMENT"
FROM "customer"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT "o_custkey" AS "O_CUSTKEY", AVG("o_totalprice") AS "AVG_TOTALPRICE"
FROM "orders"
GROUP BY "o_custkey") AS "t1" ON "customer"."c_custkey" = "t1"."O_CUSTKEY"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT "customer0"."c_custkey" AS "C_CUSTKEY", COUNT("orders0"."o_orderkey") AS "ORDER_COUNT", MAX("orders0"."o_totalprice") AS "MAX_ORDER_PRICE"
FROM "customer" AS "customer0"
LEFT JOIN "orders" AS "orders0" ON "customer0"."c_custkey" = "orders0"."o_custkey"
GROUP BY "customer0"."c_custkey") AS "t3" ON "customer"."c_custkey" = "t3"."C_CUSTKEY"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT "ps_suppkey" AS "PS_SUPPKEY", SUM("ps_supplycost" * "ps_availqty") AS "TOTAL_SUPPLYCOST"
FROM "partsupp"
GROUP BY "ps_suppkey"
HAVING SUM("ps_supplycost" * "ps_availqty") > (((SELECT AVG("ps_supplycost" * "ps_availqty")
FROM "partsupp")))) AS "t8" ON "t3"."C_CUSTKEY" = "t8"."PS_SUPPKEY"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT "s1"."s_suppkey" AS "S_SUPPKEY", "region"."r_name" AS "R_NAME"
FROM "s1"
INNER JOIN "nation" ON "s1"."s_nationkey" = "nation"."n_nationkey"
INNER JOIN "region" ON "nation"."n_regionkey" = "region"."r_regionkey") AS "t9" ON "t8"."PS_SUPPKEY" = "t9"."S_SUPPKEY"
ORDER BY 3 DESC NULLS FIRST, 4 DESC NULLS FIRST) AS "t11"
